Class ConfigurationSetting

java.lang.Object
  org.openstreetmap.osm.ConfigurationSetting

public class ConfigurationSetting
extends java.lang.Object

A ConfigurationSetting informs about a single key that can be added to the Settings. Inclusding it's name and data-type.
